<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-6470] @Grab does not work if the same dependency is used with and without a classifier</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-6470</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If a script uses the same artifact multiple times, once without a classifer and with classifier, e.g. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
@Grab(group = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;org.neo4j&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, module = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;neo4j-kernel&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, version = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;2.0.0-RC1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
@Grab(group = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;org.neo4j&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, module = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;neo4j-kernel&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, version = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;2.0.0-RC1&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, classifier = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;tests&quot;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;only the jar without a classifier is loaded.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The root cause for this is some weird behaviour in Ivy. Ivy expects for this case a single DependencyDescriptor with multiple ArtifactDescriptors. Groovy generates a DependencyDescriptor for each dependency.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve created locally a test case demoing the wrong behaviour and a bugfix as well. If desired I can sent a pull request for this. I assume the PR should be created vs master branch.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
